Taiwan to Allow Individual Chinese Tourists in June, Times Says

-- B y   Y u - H u a y   S u n
-- 
2011-03-21T23:12:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/taiwan-to-allow-individual-chinese-tourists-in-june-times-says.html
Taiwan will probably start allowing
individual Chinese tourists from Beijing and  Shanghai  in June,
the Commercial Times reported, without saying where it got the
information. The southern Chinese cities of Guangzhou and Xiamen
may also be included, the newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rebecca Evans at 
 revans6@bloomberg.net  